# Rust
target/
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock.bak

# Python (rig)
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache/
.venv/
# `pip install -e .` byproducts from the rig (see pyproject.toml).
*.egg-info/
/build/

# Editor / IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# Per-user agent harness configs (Atelier is a BYOM harness; these are *other*
# harnesses' local config that contributors may have running alongside their
# checkout — they should not ship in the repo).
.claude/
.cursor/
.aider/
.copilot/
# Harness-required project-level instruction shim (symlink → ATELIER.md).
# The real file is ATELIER.md; CLAUDE.md exists only when running under a
# host harness that hard-codes that filename.
CLAUDE.md

# Per-user permission allowlist for whichever host harness Atelier runs under.
# Each contributor regenerates locally. Shared config (no personal paths) lives
# in .atelier/settings.json which is tracked.
.atelier/settings.local.json

# On-disk session state from local runs (UUID-keyed dirs holding turn logs,
# partial completions, compaction blobs). Per-user runtime data; never tracked.
.atelier/sessions/

# Derived local indexes. Canonical memory remains in `.atelier/memory/*.md`;
# SQLite indexes are rebuildable caches and should not be committed.
.atelier/indexes/

# direnv per-project shell config. Holds developer-local secrets
# (ANTHROPIC_API_KEY, OPENAI_API_KEY) that are loaded on `cd` into the
# repo. NEVER commit — secrets-in-git is an irreversible leak that
# requires key rotation + history scrubbing to remediate.
.envrc

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Tauri
src-tauri/target/
crates/atelier-gui/gen/
crates/atelier-gui/dist/
# Frontend (Vite + Svelte + TS) — node_modules/ is the install artifact,
# dist/ the build artifact, .svelte-kit/ a tooling cache.
crates/atelier-gui/ui/node_modules/
crates/atelier-gui/ui/dist/
crates/atelier-gui/ui/.svelte-kit/
